In this Todo-list , we can simply add the list of task which we want to do 
along  width adding the list, we also push the data in the local storage
in this todo list auto sorting function  is applied which works as when we checked a task then it goes to the end of the list and other task comes up
in this we cannot set  list/ task  empty 
when the task is set empty then an alert message is shown in the website
this todo list website is responsive 
